edu.berkeley.compbio.ml.cluster

Class ClusterMove<T extends Clusterable<T>,C extends Cluster<T>>

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.berkeley.compbio.ml.cluster.ClusterMove<T,C>
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<ClusterMove<T,C>>

    public class ClusterMove<T extends Clusterable<T>,C extends Cluster<T>>
extends Object
implements Comparable<ClusterMove<T,C>>
    Represents a potential move of a sample from one cluster to another. Doesn't actually refer to the sample itself, strangely; apparently we haven't needed that yet.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
    David Soergel
